Marketing Brief -- Bertelsmann AG:
   Unit in Talks on Exercise
   Of Option on German Firm
Gruner  Jahr has management control of the Berlin
newspaper and has the option to buy the Maxwell stake or
approve the buyer of the stake. The stake "cannot be sold
without our consent," a Gruner  Jahr spokeswoman said. She
said that the company may buy the stake or sell it to
Sueddeutsche Verlag, a closely held publisher in Munich.